      "locked": false,
      "text": "Draft- When New Mo is created and not yet clicked on confirm button\n\nConfirmed- When Click on Confirmed Button\n\nIn-Progress - When Clicked on Start Button or Timmer in any work order is started\n\nTo close- When all work orders are in done state\n\nDone- When Clicked on Produce Button\n\nCancelled  - When Clicked on Cancelled",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Draft- When New Mo is created and not yet clicked on confirm button\n\nConfirmed- When Click on Confirmed Button\n\nIn-Progress - When Clicked on Start Button or Timmer in any work order is started\n\nTo close- When all work orders are in done state\n\nDone- When Clicked on Produce Button\n\nCancelled  - When Clicked on Cancelled",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
