    {
      "id": "K8hyIyw-JS8QHhLp4hCUN",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2718.443783068783,
      "y": 1203.4579344056767,
      "width": 1402.290771484375,
      "height": 300,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 90,
      "groupIds": [
        "APufwWOMt8ytNsMNy4vMY"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bMK",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 206206173,
      "version": 1672,
      "versionNonce": 1572654058,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1779788946676,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. When a new Purchase Order is created it should be created in Draft status.\n2. Vendor : Name of Vendor (store field) many2one (mandatory)\n3. Vendor  Address : Char Field max limit \n4. Creation Date: Auto populate date/time when a record is created.(here when a PO is created using new button)\n5. Responsible Person: Dropdown field, with selection of users from database\n6. Products : Dropdown Selction field to select products from Product database. (track logs)\n7. Cost Price : Populate values from Product  (track logs)\n8. Total : Ordered Qunatity* Cost Price (once recieved it should be recieved quantuity * Cost Price) (track logs)\n\nButtons:\nBack button: takes back to list view\nConfirm Button: changes Status from Draft to Confirm )(when confirm field like creation date, Vendor and Vendor address are readonly) (hide once status is change) (track logs)\nRecieve Button: 1. Change status to Fully Recieved, if Recieved Quantity= Ordered Quantity (make all fields readonly and hide Recieve button) (track logs)\n                    2. Change status to Partially Recieved if Recieved Quantity< Ordered Quantity (make all fields readonly , expect recieved quantity field. and show recieve button)\nCancel Button: Cancel Purchase Order and make all fields readonly. (track logs) ",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. When a new Purchase Order is created it should be created in Draft status.\n2. Vendor : Name of Vendor (store field) many2one (mandatory)\n3. Vendor  Address : Char Field max limit \n4. Creation Date: Auto populate date/time when a record is created.(here when a PO is created using new button)\n5. Responsible Person: Dropdown field, with selection of users from database\n6. Products : Dropdown Selction field to select products from Product database. (track logs)\n7. Cost Price : Populate values from Product  (track logs)\n8. Total : Ordered Qunatity* Cost Price (once recieved it should be recieved quantuity * Cost Price) (track logs)\n\nButtons:\nBack button: takes back to list view\nConfirm Button: changes Status from Draft to Confirm )(when confirm field like creation date, Vendor and Vendor address are readonly) (hide once status is change) (track logs)\nRecieve Button: 1. Change status to Fully Recieved, if Recieved Quantity= Ordered Quantity (make all fields readonly and hide Recieve button) (track logs)\n                    2. Change status to Partially Recieved if Recieved Quantity< Ordered Quantity (make all fields readonly , expect recieved quantity field. and show recieve button)\nCancel Button: Cancel Purchase Order and make all fields readonly. (track logs) ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
